
---

## 9. `.github/workflows/deploy.yml` (CI/CD)

```yaml
name: Deploy to Railway

on:
  push:
    branches: [ main ]

jobs:
  deploy:
    runs-on: ubuntu-latest
    steps:
      - name: Deploy via Railway CLI
        run: |
          curl -fsSL https://railway.app/install.sh | sh
          railway login
          railway up
